Rating: 3
very good and simple recipe. I generally marinate the salmon in olive oil and S + P before-hand for an extra moist variation. I did't have sake and tried a rice wine substitue(other ponzu recipes will use rice wine vinegar) but it didn't turn out the same. Also tried to double the recipe, but didn't reduce enough so was runny. I suggest sticking to the exact recipe in portion size and ingredients.

